             were indicted for <rs id="t18210606-141-off818" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210606-141-off818" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210606-141-off818" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210606-141-cd819" type="crimeDate">31st of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-141-off818 t18210606-141-cd819"></join>, one inkstand, value 6 d.; two yards of carpet, value 6 d.; one butter-boat,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182106060070"></xptr>value 6 d.; two quarts of wine, value 2 s., and two bottles, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210606-141-victim1506" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Walters
                  <interp inst="t18210606-141-victim1506" type="surname" value="Walters"></interp>
